snippet.title: Made Marion Trailer
snippet.description:
One woman, one choice, many futures.

Step into the shoes of the proud Lady Marion as fate hurtles her into the midst of historic events in the fantastical kingdom of Avalon. Will she join Robin Hood's rebels or seek to save the city of Nottingham from certain doom?

Made Marion enters early access in fall 2023!

Itch.io: https://velvet-cupcake-games.itch.io/made-marion
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1482150/Made_Marion/
